{"tid":2232518,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[中環中心自用驚西呀]戴德梁行：本港第3季寫字樓待租率逾15年來最高","createTime":"2020-10-06T12:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T14:52:29.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5399a7f07b85e8521dc9028b1075c83388f81791","tid":2232518,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T12:14:49.000Z","msg":"戴德梁行報告指，第3季本港整體寫字樓租金連跌6個季度，平均呎租62.5元，按季跌4.7%，首3季累計下跌16.1%，估計全年跌幅介乎16%至21%，中上環及金鐘區全年跌幅估計介乎20%至25%。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>期內，整體寫字樓待租率升至11.6%，創2005年首季以來最高，按季升0.9個百分點，連升4個季度。當中以九龍西16.6%空置率最高，中上環及金鐘區升至10.1%，灣仔銅鑼灣區升至11.2%。<br />\n</strong><br />\n期內寫字樓錄得負吸納量逾63萬平方呎，估計全年負吸納量逾167萬平方呎。第3季退租面積62.6萬平方呎，按季升8%。<br />\n<br />\n該行香港董事總經理蕭亮輝表示，如果新型肺炎疫情未有明顯改善，經濟持續收縮，估計中區寫字樓待租率將進一步上升，未來3個月租金或再跌約5-10%，反映企業對高價商廈承租能力弱。他相信，業主在續租時會以優惠條款留客；當有新面積招租，除了優惠條款，租金下調是必然。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553315-20201006.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553315-20201006.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKEZHjOsADYkIOf4eYSwfwZo%3D&h=3ecc3524\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553315-20201006.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0f978a93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553315-20201006.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"89db4be87db8d039ff333d18ba2760dacb00099d","tid":2232518,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T13:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36ef501d9ed25a293a1fbd604b21953ef5ab2c2","tid":2232518,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89db4be87db8d039ff333d18ba2760dacb00099d","tid":2232518,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T13:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T13:30:18.000Z","msg":"唔駛驚，仲有排跌<br />\n<br />\n九龍東大劈租，而九龍西有ICC，空置單位多到無朋友"},{"pid":"b8919787df8e10bfdd1f5f51aeefeeabe6b69f95","tid":2232518,"uid":241399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T13:32:16.000Z","msg":"可以租俾人拍 AV"},{"pid":"3449c63d499d1bd4493478c3e39f6620c658bf36","tid":2232518,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T14:52:29.000Z","msg":"出年農曆年後見真章"}]}